HEADWORD: Spoutshell
<hw>Spout"shell`</hw> <pr>(-sh⟦ecr⟧l`)</pr>, <pos>n.</pos>
<fld>(Zool.)</fld> <def>Any marine gastropod shell of the genus
<gen>Apporhais</gen> having an elongated siphon. See <xex>Illust.</xex>
under <er>Rostrifera</er>.</def>⟦br⟧
[<source>1913 Webster</source>]</p>

